This software includes or downloads the following third-party components:

1. MediaPipe FaceLandmarker
   Source:  https://github.com/google-ai-edge/mediapipe
   License: Apache License 2.0
   Used for: face detection and 478-point facial landmark extraction

2. facex_nano (facex-engine/facex, tag facex-nano-1.0)
   Source:  https://github.com/facex-engine/facex/releases/tag/facex-nano-1.0
   License: Apache License 2.0 (code and weights)
   Used for: 256-D face embedding (NCHW [1,3,112,112], ArcFace-trained, LFW 95.62%)
   Data caveat: Weights were trained on MS1M-RefineV2. The dataset itself
   has restricted usage terms. The weights are independently Apache-2.0 licensed.
   Consumers should evaluate whether the data-lineage restriction affects their
   specific use case.

3. onnxruntime-web
   Source:  https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime
   License: MIT License
   Used for: WASM-based ONNX model inference in the browser

Model weights are NOT bundled in this package. They are downloaded separately
via models/download.sh. Consumers are responsible for compliance with the
applicable model licenses.
